    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br><strong>你的目标是找到上锁房门的钥匙，从而逃出房子。一个疯狂的卡哇伊女孩会阻止你这么做。你可以暂时躲在谷仓的箱子里、床底下或衣柜里，但一般来说，如果她发现了你，你最好赶紧跑。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/62b7185ee28546368119d5634922a344.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色 </h2><br><strong>在主菜单中，你可以从 14 个追逐你的角色中选择一个。别让他们追上你！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.webm?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/c9d4d1a7af0b973adb1600a55a3d9abb.mp4?t=1721041621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >氛围：</h2><br><strong>你被困在一栋乡间别墅里，有人在追你，你需要找到一条出路。这是一款在狭小空间内捉迷藏的游戏，您有五条命，即五次尝试开门逃生的机会。如果失败，关卡将重新开始。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/60541c3c4b31052b8ea10afd2b06f505.poster.avif?t=1721041621\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018830/extras/60541c3c4b31052b8